  "prompt": "Are there any NGO's in vijaynagar or rajajinagar?",
  "response": "Yes, there are several NGOs operating in the Vijaynagar and Rajajinagar areas of Bangalore. Here are a few notable ones:\n\n### Vijaynagar:\n\n1. **Seva Sahayog Foundation**\n   - **Location:** Near Deve Gowda Petrol Bunk, Vijaynagar, Bangalore\n   - **Focus:** Education, health, and community development\n   - **Contact:** You can find their contact details on their official website or through a quick search.\n\n2. **Swami Vivekananda Youth Movement (SVYM)**\n   - **Location:** They have a presence in various parts of Bangalore, including nearby areas to Vijaynagar.\n   - **Focus:** Health, education, socio-economic development\n   - **Contact:** Check their official website for specific contact information.\n\n### Rajajinagar:\n\n1. **Sadhana School**\n   - **Location:** 1st 'N' Block, Rajajinagar, Bangalore\n   - **Focus:** Education and vocational training for children with intellectual disabilities\n   - **Contact:** Available on their official website.\n\n2. **Spastic Society of Karnataka**\n   - **Location:** 1st Cross, 1st Stage, 1st Phase, Gokula, Rajajinagar, Bangalore\n   - **Focus:** Rehabilitation and empowerment of individuals with cerebral palsy, intellectual disabilities, and other neurological conditions\n   - **Contact:** Their official website provides detailed contact information.\n\n3. **Rotary Bangalore Rajajinagar**\n   - **Location:** Rotary House, 1st Main Road, 1st Block, Rajajinagar, Bangalore\n   - **Focus:** Various community service projects including health, education, and environmental initiatives\n   - **Contact:** You can find their contact details through their official channels.\n\nTo get more detailed and up-to-date information, I recommend visiting the official websites of these NGOs or contacting them directly. Additionally, you can check local directories or community boards for more NGOs in these areas.",
